<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idcad19220-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s5568"><num value="5568">§ 5568.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idcad19221-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s5568/a"><num value="a">(a)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">General</inline>.—</heading><chapeau>The following amounts may be appropriated to the Secretary of Transportation:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idcad19222-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s5568/a/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> not more than $15,000,000 to carry out section 5562(a)(1) and (3) of this title.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idcad19223-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s5568/a/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> not more than $2,500,000 to carry out <ref href="/us/usc/t49/s5562/a/2">section 5562(a)(2) of this title</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idcad19224-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s5568/a/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> not more than $2,500,000 to carry out <ref href="/us/usc/t49/s5562/a/4">section 5562(a)(4) of this title</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0" id="idcad19225-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s5568/b"><num value="b">(b)</num><heading> <inline class="small-caps">Availability of Amounts</inline>.—</heading><content>Amounts appropriated to carry out this chapter remain available until expended.</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idcad19226-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70">(<ref href="/us/pl/103/272/s1/d">Pub. L. 103–272, § 1(d)</ref>, <date date="1994-07-05">July 5, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/854">108 Stat. 854</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
