</html:tbody>
</html:table>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">In subsection (a), before clause (1), the words “to the Secretary of Transportation” are added for clarity and consistency in this chapter.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">In subsection (b), the words “to carry out” are substituted for “for the purpose set forth . . . in” for consistency in the revised title and with other titles of the United States Code.</p>
